ğŸš€ How to run

1. Create a folder, put index.html + app.js inside.


2. Replace 0xYourERC20Token and 0xYourGameContract with your token + game contract addresses.


3. Open index.html in a browser with MetaMask.


4. Click Connect Wallet â†’ Spin.



âš ï¸ Right now the â€œrewardâ€ is front-end only (fake random). To make it real, you need a backend or VRF that signs outcomes and a reward contract that verifies + pays.


